#ROOM
Vnum     20080
Name     &rShadowforge Gateway&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The humid heat of Blackrock Mountain becomes an oppressive, 
sulfurous furnace as you step through the heavy iron portcullis. 
You stand at the beginning of a wide, descending stone ramp 
that leads into the dark heart of the Dark Iron capital. 
The air vibrates with the distant, rhythmic pounding of a 
thousand hammers.
~
#EXIT
Direction out~
ToRoom    36560
Desc      Return to the Hall of the Mountain.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20081
Desc      The descending ramp.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20081
Name     &rThe Entry Ramp&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive thoroughfare built for the passage of entire armies. 
The walls are high and reinforced with plates of dark iron. 
Gratings in the floor allow the heat from the magma rivers 
below to rise, keeping the ramp at a blistering temperature.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20080
Desc      The gateway.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20082
Desc      The crossroads of the deep.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20021 10 20081
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20082
Name     &rThe Crossroads of the Deep&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The main road splits here. To the east, a heavily guarded 
gate leads toward the Detention Block and the Ring of Law. 
To the north, the road continues toward the industrial 
heart of the city.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20081
Desc      The entry ramp.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20083
Desc      Toward the Detention Block.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20095
Desc      Toward the industrial district.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20024 5 20082
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20083
Name     &rDetention Block - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The ceiling here is low and the air is thick with the scent 
of unwashed bodies and despair. Stone cells line both sides 
of the hallway, their iron bars glowing faintly in the dim 
magical light.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20082
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20084
Desc      Deep into the cell block.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20000 10 20083
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20084
Name     &rDetention Block - Central Hall&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A wide intersection where several cell wings meet. A large, 
central station for the wardens is located here, filled 
with racks of manacles and heavy batons.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20083
Desc      The cell block entry.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20085
Desc      The interrogation chamber.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20086
Desc      The kennel entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20000 10 20084
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20085
Name     &rThe Interrogation Chamber&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls are hung with various terrifying tools of torture. 
A massive stone rack sits in the center of the room. High 
Interrogator Gerstahn stands here, preparing her next 
subject for questioning.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20084
Desc      The central hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20002 1 20085
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20086
Name     &rThe Houndmaster's Kennels&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large, smelly chamber filled with the sounds of barking 
and snarling. The floor is covered in gnawed bones and 
matted fur. Houndmaster Grebmar oversees his pack from 
a raised platform.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20084
Desc      The central hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20087
Desc      Toward the Ring of Law.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20004 1 20086
Reset M 0 20001 10 20086
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20087
Name     &rThe Arena Tunnel&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A narrow, stone tunnel leading toward the city's arena. 
The roar of a crowd can be heard echoing through the 
shaft, becoming louder with every step.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20086
Desc      The kennels.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20088
Desc      The Ring of Law.~
#ENDEXIT
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20088
Name     &rThe Ring of Law&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     You stand in the center of a massive circular pit. High above, 
tiers of stone seating are filled with jeering Dark Iron 
spectators. This is the place of final judgment for those 
who break the Emperor's laws.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20087
Desc      The entry tunnel.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20089
Desc      The spectator stands.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20027 1 20088
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20089
Name     &rThe Arena Stands - Lower&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Rows of stone benches occupied by rowdy citizens. They 
throw garbage and insults at the combatants in the pit below.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20088
Desc      Return to the pit.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction up~
ToRoom    20090
Desc      The upper stands.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20026 10 20088
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20090
Name     &rThe Arena Stands - Upper&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A high stone balcony overlooking the entire arena. From 
here, the nobles of Shadowforge watch the spectacles 
with detached amusement.
~
#EXIT
Direction down~
ToRoom    20089
Desc      The lower stands.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20110
Desc      Toward the city residential district.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20036 5 20090
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20091
Name     &rThe East Garrison - Entrance&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A heavily fortified stone chamber housing the primary 
guard contingent for the eastern gate. Racks of 
sharp iron halberds line the walls.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20083
Desc      The cell block.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20021 10 20091
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20092
Name     &rThe East Garrison - Armory&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The walls are covered in shields, plate armor, and 
magical crystals. Dark Iron weaponmasters work here, 
ensuring the garrison is always battle-ready.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20091
Desc      The garrison entrance.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20025 1 20092
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20093
Name     &rThe Shadowed Cell&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors dark~
Desc     A small, isolated cell far away from the others. The 
only light comes from the faint glow of the iron bars.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20084
Desc      The cell block hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 20054 1 20093
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20094
Name     &rDetention Block - Hidden Passage&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A narrow, dusty crawlway behind a loose stone in one 
of the cells. It bypasses the main warden station.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20084
Desc      Return to the hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20029 10 20094
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20095
Name     &rThe Slag Run&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A long, hot corridor that runs parallel to the main industrial 
lines. Pipes overhead carry molten metal, and the 
rhythm of steam valves is constant. Lord Roccor can 
often be seen wandering this hall.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20082
Desc      The crossroads.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20096
Desc      Toward the Black Forge.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20003 1 20095
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20096
Name     &rThe Black Forge - Entry&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The temperature here is incredible. A river of lava flows 
through the center of the room, powering a massive, 
enchanted anvil. Lord Incendius stands guard over the 
sacred site.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20095
Desc      The slag run.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20100
Desc      Toward the Crafting Hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20008 1 20096
Reset M 0 20038 10 20096
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20100
Name     &rThe Hall of Crafting - South&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A massive factory where the clan's finest smiths work. 
The air is filled with sparks and the roar of dozens 
of magical furnaces.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20096
Desc      The Black Forge.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20101
Desc      The Hall of Crafting North.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20030 10 20100
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20101
Name     &rThe Hall of Crafting - North&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     This section of the hall is dedicated to the creation of 
war golems. Massive half-finished metal shells hang 
from iron chains in the ceiling. Golem Lord Argelmach 
oversees the delicate work from a high platform.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20100
Desc      The southern hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20102
Desc      The Manufacturing Wing.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20012 1 20101
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20102
Name     &rThe Manufacturing Wing&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     Smaller workshops line this hallway, each focused on a 
specific part of the Dark Iron war machine, from 
rifles to magical armor plating.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20101
Desc      The main hall.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20103
Desc      The High Architect's Sanctum.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20006 10 20102
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20103
Name     &rThe High Architect's Sanctum&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A large room decorated with blueprints and stone models. 
Fineous Darkvire stands here, Conferring with several 
master smiths.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20102
Desc      The manufacturing wing.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20007 1 20103
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20104
Name     &rThe Steam Works&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A noisy chamber filled with high-pressure boilers and 
rattling steam pipes. The visibility is low due to 
the constant mist.
~
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20100
Desc      The crafting hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20030 5 20104
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20105
Name     &rThe Slag Pit - Central&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A deep, circular pit where the waste from the forge 
is dumped. Fireguard destroyers move through the 
glowing embers, consuming the energy within.
~
#EXIT
Direction north~
ToRoom    20096
Desc      The Black Forge.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20005 5 20105
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20106
Name     &rCrafting Hall Overflow A&d~
Sector   inside~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     A side storage area filled with crates of refined iron 
and thorium bars.
~
#EXIT
Direction south~
ToRoom    20100
Desc      The crafting hall.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 20048 10 20106
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20110
Name     &rShadowforge City - West Street&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The start of the capital's residential area. Stone houses 
are built into the cavern walls, each glowing with 
soft blue light from the streetlamps. Dwarf citizens 
hurry about their business.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20090
Desc      The arena balcony.~
#ENDEXIT
#EXIT
Direction east~
ToRoom    20111
Desc      The Central Plaza.~
#ENDEXIT
Reset M 0 20023 10 20110
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20111
Name     &rThe Shadowforge Plaza&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The heart of the Dark Iron capital. A massive statue of 
Thaurissan the Great stands in the center. To the 
north, the impressive entrance to the Grim Guzzler 
tavern is visible.
~
#EXIT
Direction west~
ToRoom    20110
