#ENDEXIT
Reset O 0 20051 1 20114
#ENDROOM

#ROOM
Vnum     20115
Name     &rThe Grim Guzzler - Entrance&d~
Sector   city~
Flags    indoors~
Desc     The sound of drinking songs and smashing mugs is 
